00:51:15.465 --> 00:51:16.535
sales, et cetera.

1026
00:51:16.915 --> 00:51:18.895
We have around 2000 contractors.

1027
00:51:19.315 --> 00:51:20.855
Uh, the vast majority, well the majority

1028
00:51:20.855 --> 00:51:22.455
of those in New Zealand, um,

