00:54:04.875 --> 00:54:06.215
And the average income

1094
00:54:06.275 --> 00:54:09.655
for a Freightways courier contract is $507 a day.

1095
00:54:10.155 --> 00:54:13.375
At the moment. What we do is we gear those payments

1096
00:54:13.435 --> 00:54:14.615
around a daily rate.

1097
00:54:15.195 --> 00:54:18.375
And so while we have no issue in principle

1098
